text.tspan: Kaya identity: drivers of CO₂ emissions, World
Percentage change in the four parameters of the Kaya Identity, which determine total CO₂ emissions. Emissions
include fossil fuel and industry emissions. Land use change is not included.
Note: GDP per capita is measured in 2011 international-$ (PPP). This adjusts for inflation and cross-country price differences.
Data source: Our World in Data based on Global Carbon Project; UN; BP; World Bank; Maddison Project Database
